{"tid":611682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又冧網] 中國聯通疑又死機   客戶訴苦不能上網打電話如陷孤島","createTime":"2018-03-31T09:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T11:49:39.000Z","uid":174882,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"81eb42acf5e3454d4d944c1f615b93fa85f28e9b","tid":611682,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/171852_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F171852_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c04f023a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇網絡點&ldquo;陷&rdquo;連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2b6f516f92fd6575ad68970a4fa0beb71b8be6","tid":611682,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:30:42.000Z","msg":"電訊商中國聯通懷疑又「死機」？！繼上月27日曾出現故障令大量客戶無法使用電話及上網服務後( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Cq4uMc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Cq4uMc&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=6c1cffc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Cq4uMc</a> )，中國聯通今午又疑再出問題，大量香港的中國聯通客戶在網上包括中聯通官方fb留言訴苦指通訊失靈，包括「上唔到網」、「打唔到電話」，有顧客質疑「有冇壞得咁密啊？」有事主親身到門市求助，但無果，並指已出現排隊的人龍；有人怒斥中國聯通服務差，指不足兩個月內兩度發生嚴重故障實難以接受，要求電訊商「回水」或「解約」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者正致電中國聯通了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，記者到荃灣南豐廣場的中國聯通門市了解，有顧客正向職員投訴：「今朝打極都打唔到電話呀！」職員透露，電話話音服務故障，但上網服務如常。<br />\n<br />\n中國聯通在官方fb貼文表示，收到個別客人反映，話音服務曾經出現問題，現正恢復中。如仍有問題，請重啟電話，對造成任何不便，深表歉意。如仍未能使用，請致電客服熱線2122 1188，或聯絡在線客服 <a href=\"Https://www.cuniq.com/hk/contact-us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=Https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuniq.com%2Fhk%2Fcontact-us.html&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ef0ba81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Https://www.cuniq.com/hk/contact-us.html</a>"},{"pid":"6baf067887aff58b27551c14eb0161d7336bdf58","tid":611682,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"还有党<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de968d6b69a66e1ac994f6346ce3b67f356faafb","tid":611682,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6baf067887aff58b27551c14eb0161d7336bdf58","tid":611682,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"还有党<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"只限一次<br />\n再殘體死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}